imdb.plot outline: WTFark! is a satirical comedy news web series from Larry King's Ora TV. (Think "The Daily Show" for weird and local news reports.) Hosted by gifted comedian Mike Rylander, WTFark features the weirdest, most head-scratching, and just plain funniest news stories making the rounds on social media. Featuring headlines from Fark.com, the Internet's first and most popular news community, and receiving additional distribution from AOL and The Huffington Post, WTFark reaches over half a million viewers each month, and that number is growing fast...
imdb.title: WTFark!
plot: Host/Writer Mike Rylander takes us through fark.com news stories with clever, snarky edge. Produced by OraTV. Distributed by AOL and The Huffington Post.::Anonymous
